$ ./demo_object.ts --help
Tool usage description here

Usage: <script path> [Options] [--] [command [cmd args]]

Commands:
  main <name>            [default]
  up
  down <force> <timeout> down cmd description

Options:
 -h, --help    Show this help                          [default: false]
 -r, --retry   number of retries                           [default: 2]
     --dry-run perform a trial run with no changes made [default: true]

$ ./demo_object.ts
main command undefined 2
up command

$ ./demo_object.ts -r 5 --dry-run true down true 10
down command { force: true, timeout: 10, retry: 5, dryRun: true }
